{"tid":314701,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家打邊爐係點打？","createTime":"2017-07-09T12:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T11:43:47.000Z","uid":99209,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b174243f553e4340ab6df611e2a814d89480672","tid":314701,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"次次同朋友任食邊邊，一開始就落肉、丸、豬紅個D，尤其係D碟入面仲有水就一野鏟落去<br />\n搞到成個爐勁多唔知乜野浮起，一堆泡，極為噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後總會有條傻仔慢慢撈翻起d泡落空杯，但都係照舊咁落野&hellip;<br />\n後期先有人落菜，D菜就吸撚曬d泡，真係你食埋我個份&hellip;<br />\n成晚我就睇住D水既顏色變黎變去，魔藥學咩老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反我屋企係先落菜同血比較少既肉，到最後D水重係清，可以飲"},{"pid":"403aa9171d3e4d43d848dbec9d950be4e27ab606","tid":314701,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"你唔識落？"},{"pid":"4afac5582e6e6388dd2d2245ef4bb20e8ab4e51b","tid":314701,"uid":72475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"用拳頭"},{"pid":"89bd4b24eb77521da1cb96e36393d1a947d99041","tid":314701,"uid":25758,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:50:35.000Z","msg":"On9 打個邊爐都咁撚講究"},{"pid":"659e78598645acee2d31c1675de1e248855e296e","tid":314701,"uid":53798,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"一班人係咁嫁啦, 咁有要求就自己要一個爐"},{"pid":"1347cfdc4594eb987cd35ddf790d10da174ed821","tid":314701,"uid":87433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎"},{"pid":"420cc6fbc6babc06eda62e2b78de6df301885294","tid":314701,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"落出前一丁先"},{"pid":"44bcd7b064517067551b14cf9b1927a1e4de1281","tid":314701,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:53:33.000Z","msg":"我緊係有落啦，個爐咁鬼細<br />\n搞唔得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d382183bb1eb9756bfbff283024d1355bd73955","tid":314701,"uid":99209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>任嗌架喎</blockquote><br />\n我知呀"},{"pid":"2b75a0c0115b93bba20aa7cf620bb2f5ab4308ec","tid":314701,"uid":99209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 打個邊爐都咁撚講究</blockquote><br />\n睇落好樣衰呀嘛<br />\n成日都係堆肉色既泡夾起d野，真係好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa95171cca599f20238f7c0c5e247d93c45ac3eb","tid":314701,"uid":38550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"料同湯底問題<br />\n我喺屋企都係落肉先唔會有泡<br />\n出面食都唔係間間有泡<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係出面有啲地方唔知用乜腌啲肉<br />\n再加上個垃圾湯底先會咁"},{"pid":"f1b1b592fe764cada5e4aa6ce7166d43f36cd0d7","tid":314701,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>料同湯底問題<br />\n我喺屋企都係落肉先唔會有泡<br />\n出面食都唔係間間有泡<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係出面有啲地方唔知用乜腌啲肉<br />\n再加上個垃圾湯底先會咁</blockquote><br />\n屋企都係係街市鳩買蕃茄、瓜、蘿白咁<br />\nD泡主要係D血同脂肪&hellip;見親D豬紅一落，成爐都風雲色變"},{"pid":"3d806097be655091574914329e45456d65cc26c4","tid":314701,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"係個爐要安全呀"},{"pid":"6ad7b178ca63ef915056f8e58609e70c1b6e324e","tid":314701,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:17:05.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66305706197ad24175641da3682f20218a2e30d","tid":314701,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"見到魔藥學唔爭氣笑咗"},{"pid":"e4523e05ace4e05c0944b78e978ee323da1e2c71","tid":314701,"uid":119122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"打邊爐最緊要個爐"},{"pid":"917d0a6e2e4dfc4d3b4f82ef3a7f5f05c1dcfa6b","tid":314701,"uid":3269