0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"任食邊爐都係大家一齊落架嘛<br />\n只係由細都大都發覺好多人對d泡無乜所謂，一味照落<br />\n又食得好過癮<br />\n唔係無試過，但邊有可能控制人地點落，咪唯有定期整走d泡囉<br />\n唔通你地覺得有d泡係上面會好睇又好食d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有口水又有血水"},{"pid":"f9f8a78929174c2461d0616a21bc4cd4b5a65f24","tid":314701,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:08:03.000Z","msg":"近幾年屋企都冇打邊爐<br />\n自己一個人出街打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7a2ba3d248561c2d5942b4af94119c20ddd43f","tid":314701,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚識食WO屌你"},{"pid":"b2af74c215625c77605d7558257194d37f0a714f","tid":314701,"uid":72608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"成班人食緊係爭住食肥牛,丸果d肉先,<br />\n食肉食到咁上下先食返D菜<br />\n一開始食菜根本冇feel"},{"pid":"6f553bc4fade580fc68f590cbd8a5fa1736624f1","tid":314701,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:18:46.000Z","msg":"打邊爐最緊要係咩呀<br />\n：xxxxxxxxx<br />\n：打邊爐最緊要個煲唔好大過個爐"},{"pid":"19975bec806875d5844c2dad130285262a06f81a","tid":314701,"uid":92314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:01:59.000Z","msg":"卜尸 火廿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6432dc8dbdd52e9887c0487f506014e9ab6190d3","tid":314701,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:45:15.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"26f8d698293a4615df1e9f74f4e4065d07b2b58e","tid":314701,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"劣牛先會多泡 血水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其垃圾肥牛"},{"pid":"f7c8af8612bed7e4b97c5030050e8c67504b3e11","tid":314701,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite